parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "NekRS",
  "software": [
    "Nek5000",
    "OpenMPI",
    "CUDA",
    "Cray PE-X86 Milan",
    "Cray PE-Accel Nvidia 80",
    "NVIDIA HPC SDK",
    "libFabirc",
    "PrgEnv-gnu",
    "Spack"
  ],
  "resource": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "cores": 8,
    "gpu": 4,
    "queue": "prod",
    "walltime": "hh:mm:ss"
  },
  "libraries": [
    "libfabric",
    "cmake",
    "libstdc++",
    "MPICH",
    "CUDA"
  ],
  "environment": {
    "NEKRS_HOME": "/path/to/NekRS",
    "NEKRS_GPU_MPI": 1,
    "NEKRS_CACHE_BCAST": 1,
    "NEKRS_LOCAL_TMP_DIR": "/local/scratch",
    "MPICH_MPIIO_HINTS": "*:striping_unit=16777216:striping_factor=64:romio_cb_write=enable:romio_ds_write=disable:romio_no_indep_rw=true",
    "MPICH_MPIIO_STATS": 1,
    "MPICH_GPU_SUPPORT_ENABLED": 1,
    "MPICH_OFI_NIC_POLICY": "NUMA",
    "FI_OFI_RXM_RX_SIZE": 32768,
    "LD_PRELOAD": "/opt/cray/pe/gcc/12.2.0/snos/lib64/libstdc++.so.6",
    "CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES": "gpu_id",
    "PROJ_ID": "project_id"
  },
  "usage": "[PROJ_ID] [QUEUE] $0 <casename> <number of compute nodes> <hh:mm:ss>"
}
```
